HEADWORD: Hares-foot fern
<hw>Hare's"-foot` fern`</hw> <pr>(-f⟦oocr⟧t` f⟦etil⟧rn`)</pr>.
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A species of fern (<spn>Davallia
